<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV48">
<l>melliya lākkaik kirumi kuruviṉ miḷirtantāṅkē</l>
<l>celliya celkait tulakaiyeṉ kāṇumeṉ ṉāluntaṉṉaic</l>
<l>colliya cūḻaṟ ṟirumā lavaṉkavi yātukaṟṟēṉ</l>
<l>palliyiṉ colluñcol lākkoḷva tōvuṇṭu paṇṭupaṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like a maggot with body of soft nature turning in a sore,</l>
<l>it goes as it goes, how will it see the world? Timumāl, with [his] intention</l>
<l>for me too to speak about him all days, poems on him, what have I learned?</l>
<l>Is even the word of the lizard taken as unspoken? It was [so] in all former times.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
